      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All specimens sourced from production lots; CMM measurements confirm dimensional conformance within ±0.05 mm of nominal for critical features (rod diameter, screw shank diameter, set-screw torque). Sample variability characterised by coefficient of variation <4% for stiffness."
