      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standardised load configuration (axial compression-bending at 5°). Although this replicates the regulatory submission condition, only one load condition was explored, limiting coverage of the broader physiological loading space. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory context where F1717 is the recognised standard comparator."
