      "rationale": "Normalised error metric E/uval computed for each QoI using combined experimental uncertainty (inter-specimen variability, measurement uncertainty) and model prediction uncertainty. All three QoIs (stiffness: 1.12, yield force: 0.87, force at 40 mm: 1.41) satisfy E/uval < 1.96. Percentage differences all below 10% pre-registered bound. Output comparison criterion fully met."
