    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is accepted. The majority of credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The one factor below required level (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the shortfall is judged acceptable given that ASTM F1717 is the FDA-recognised standard protocol for this device class and no additional load conditions are required for the intended regulatory submission. The model inputs factor was reviewed and found consistent with applicable practice; the assessment team is satisfied that the overall evidence base is sufficient to support the intended use of the FEA model for this COU.",
